<section class="mx-auto sm:max-w-4xl">

  <h1 class="font-black text-6xl md:text-9xl">I like big fonts and I cannot lie</h1>

  <p class="mt-4 mx-auto text-lg sm:max-w-2xl">Other front-enders can't deny! When a site loads up with a big ol' font...</p>

  <p class="mt-4 mx-auto text-lg sm:max-w-2xl">Anyways, welcome to my little slice of the internet. I'm Dan Denney, a front-end dev at <a class="link" href="https://www.datacamp.com">DataCamp</a> and all around fan design and dev.</p>

</section>

<section class="pt-32">

  <h2 class="mb-8 mx-auto font-black text-5xl sm:max-w-4xl md:text-8xl">Recent Blog Posts</h2>

  <nav class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center pb-12 posts">
    {% set homePosts = collections.posts | reverse %}
    {% for homePost in homePosts.slice(0, 3) %}
      <a class="duration-300 relative transition-transform md:m-4 hover:transform hover:scale-105" href="{{ homePost.url | url }}">
        {{ homePost.data.poster | safe }}
      </a>
    {% endfor %} 
  </nav>

</section>

